ng Cost – 250mana<br>Casting Time W/O Casting Haste (AA&amp;Focus) – 3.5 sec<br>Casting Time W/ Casting Haste (AA&amp;Focus) – 3.5 sec (below 4.0 so no effect)<br>Spell Dmg – 1200pts<br><br><br>So effectively, you only get a better mana ratio with the new spell at a cost of an incredibly rare spell that is slower than the less improved version.<br><br>It seems quite clear that when they first designed this spell, focus items and AA abilities to give spell haste weren’t considered (especially the 4sec min).<br><br>Considering anyone that gets this spell will most likely already have the AA and Focus items, I don’t think the following request is unfair or unreasonable. <br><br><br><br>Requested Solution:<br>Either make the spell work with the Casting Haste or change the timing so that it’s equivalently faster counting haste modifications.<br><br><br><br> <p><p><font color="#800000"><b>SertainX T'Kell - Sorcerer – <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=130970">My Gear</a> – <a href="http://www.sertain.com">My Site </a> – <a href="http://www.clubfu.com">Club Fu </a></b></font></p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uakser.showPublicProfile?language=EN>aKSer</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/6/02 8:18:10 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=326.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Name:  Ancient: Destruction of Ice  - Needs change IMO</span><hr size=1> Does this spell have a long recast time like soltice? and a 50 manna difference is helpfull<br>figuring your about average with 4000ish manna pool total you can get a total of 13 spears,and 16 of the ancient spells,thats 3600 damage not including if ya have improved damage 3.But yes it is