rap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/umiriai.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Miriai</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/15/02 1:46:18 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=326.topic&index=6>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://members.shaw.ca/wblew/images/icon.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: heh</span><hr size=1> My feelings? Given they both have the 13s recast time, the improved mana efficiency of the ancient version is worthwhile.<br><br>Why? With longer fights being the vogue (ssra/VT mobs) mana efficiency is more important than ever. Remember that efficiency both improves the value of both our mana pool and our mana regeneration rate.<br><br>Would I be happy with that ancient spell? Yes I would. Of course, I'd swap it for an EER or GSS without hesitation. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p>-----<a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=260310 target=blank>Miriai</a>, Saryrn</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/unaanaaneebooboo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Naanaan Eebooboo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/28/02 9:45:53 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=326.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Name:  Ancient: Destruction of Ice  - Needs change IMO</span><hr size=1> By itself, yeah, the spell isn't all that cracked up to be.<br><br>But remember that you can have both the ancient spell and regular Ice spear loaded at the same time. Given the 13s recast on both spells, this is pretty damn good.<br><br>But yeah, that casting time thing, if correct, really does suck. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.showPrevMessage?topicID=326.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.showNextMessage?topicID=326.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=326.topic&index=7><img src=http://www.graffe.com/messageboard/add_reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.emailToFriend?topicID=326.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.threadControl?topicID=326.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=326.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=326.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub23.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post>